members.signatureAfterChange: int gtk_test_expand_row (int tree, int iter, int path)
diff: +	* Bug in GTK.  test-expand-row does not get called for each row
+	* in an expand all operation.  The fix is to block the initial
+	* expansion and only expand a single level.
